data.description: Newly Renovated Cottage, that seamlessly blends past & present. Ready for you to make it home! Step into timeless elegance with the beautiful woodwork, which adds a touch of classic charm and character, showcasing the craftsmanship of a bygone era. Enjoy hardwood floors throughout, modern bathroom and kitchens with new stainless-steel appliances. This property also features a front porch, double living room, 4 bedrooms 2 1/2 Bathrooms, full basement, yard and off-street parking. New roof, newly fenced in yard.
